data.description:
Welcome to your dream mid-century modern home nestled in the highly sought-after neighborhood of Hampden Heights West. This charming and cool residence offers a perfect blend of mid-century modern architecture and modern updates, making it an ideal haven for contemporary living.

Located in a serene cul-de-sac, this spacious home boasts 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, providing ample space for comfortable living. The finished basement adds versatility to the layout, offering additional room for recreation or entertainment.

Step inside to discover a thoughtfully updated interior, where mid-century charm meets contemporary convenience. The home features stylish updates throughout, ensuring a seamless blend of modern comforts.

Situated on a large lot, this property offers plenty of outdoor space for relaxation and entertaining. The backyard is a blank canvas ready for your personal touch! Enjoy the tranquility of the surrounding landscape, with the renowned Hampden Heights trail practically at your doorstep, ideal for outdoor enthusiasts and nature lovers.

The home offers easy access to I-25, making commuting a breeze. Nearby amenities include the convenience of Whole Foods, the Happy Canyon Shopping Center, and access to Bible Park via the trail. The close proximity to Cherry Creek Reservoir and Dog Park provides endless opportunities for outdoor adventures.

Indulge in the vibrant culinary scene with an array of great restaurants just moments away. Whether you're seeking outdoor recreation, shopping, or dining, this location offers the perfect balance of convenience and leisure.

Don't miss your chance to own this quintessential mid-century modern gem in the heart of Hampden Heights West.
